OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry end to
OL,6,Fthe day with some sunshine. Shetland
OL,7,Fwill remain dry with clear spells
OL,8,Fovernight but some showers will spread
OL,9,Feast over Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA lot of dry and bright
OL,12,Fweather with light winds. A few
OL,13,Fshowers over Orkney, spreading to
OL,14,FShetland in the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry with sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,18,Fwith the odd shower. Dry, bright and
OL,19,Fbreezy on Thursday, perhaps some rain
OL,20,Flater. Sunshine and showers on Friday.
